desiredState.description: The Auto-Tune desired state for the domain. Valid values: `ENABLED` or `DISABLED`.

maintenanceSchedules.description: Configuration block for Auto-Tune maintenance windows. Can be specified multiple times for each maintenance window. Detailed below.

rollbackOnDisable.description: Whether to roll back to default Auto-Tune settings when disabling Auto-Tune. Valid values: `DEFAULT_ROLLBACK` or `NO_ROLLBACK`.
